it looks like she just multiplied
both sides times a number.

00:04:14.750 --> 00:04:17.485
And it looks like that
number, she clearly multiplied

00:04:17.485 --> 00:04:20.917
the right-hand side times negative eight.

00:04:20.917 --> 00:04:23.151
So times negative eight.

00:04:23.151 --> 00:04:26.884
Negative one times negative
eight is positive eight.

00:04:26.884 --> 00:04:29.051
And it looks like she also multiplied

00:04:29.051 --> 00:04:30.618
the left-hand side by negative eight.

